# Project Overview

The Unified Ticket Booking System is a centralized web application that allows users to book multiple types of tickets (Train, Bus, Flight, Movie, Hotel) from a single platform.

🔹 In this mini project, the Hotel Booking Module is fully functional.
🔹 Other ticket modules are included as conceptual/demo modules.

This system reduces user effort by eliminating the need to visit multiple platforms for ticket booking.

## Features

🔐 User Registration & Login

🏨 Hotel Booking (Fully Functional)

🚆 Train Booking (Demo)

🚌 Bus Booking (Demo)

✈ Flight Booking (Demo)

🎬 Movie Ticket Booking (Demo)

📄 E-Ticket Generation

💳 Payment Integration (Demo Mode)

📊 Admin Dashboard

📜 Booking History

🔍 Search & Filter Options

